{"id":"b0a7c0a5638d","content":"Recorded at Microsoft Build, Ryan welcomes Sarah Bird, Microsoft’s Chief Product Officer for Responsible AI, about how we can build and use AI responsibly with the NIST approach, why most irresponsible AI comes from experimentation without thought of impact, and how Microsoft is researching thoughtful human/AI workflow design to reduce unnecessary escalation. ​​​​‌﻿‍﻿​‍​‍‌‍﻿﻿‌﻿​‍‌‍‍‌‌‍‌﻿‌‍‍‌‌‍﻿‍​‍​‍​﻿‍‍​‍​‍‌﻿​﻿‌‍​‌‌‍﻿‍‌‍‍‌‌﻿‌​‌﻿‍‌​‍﻿‍‌‍‍‌‌‍﻿﻿​‍​‍​‍﻿​​‍​‍‌‍‍​‌﻿​‍‌‍‌‌‌‍‌‍​‍​‍​﻿‍‍​‍​‍‌‍‍​‌﻿‌​‌﻿‌​‌﻿​​‌﻿​﻿​﻿‍‍​‍﻿﻿​‍﻿﻿‌‍​﻿‌‍﻿‌‌﻿​﻿​‍﻿‍‌﻿​﻿‌﻿‌​‌‍​‌‌‍​﻿‌‍‍﻿‌‍﻿﻿‌﻿‌‍‌‍‌‌‌﻿​‍‌‍‌‍‌‍﻿​‌‍﻿﻿‌﻿‌﻿​‍﻿‍‌‍​﻿‌‍﻿﻿​‍﻿﻿‌‍‍‌‌‍﻿‍‌﻿‌​‌‍‌‌‌‍﻿‍‌﻿‌​​‍﻿﻿‌‍‌‌‌‍‌​‌‍‍‌‌﻿‌​​‍﻿﻿‌‍﻿‌‌‍﻿﻿‌‍‌​‌‍‌‌​﻿﻿‌‌﻿​​‌﻿​‍‌‍‌‌‌﻿​﻿‌‍‌‌‌‍﻿‍‌﻿‌​‌‍​‌‌﻿‌​‌‍‍‌‌‍﻿﻿‌‍﻿‍​﻿‍﻿‌‍‍‌‌‍‌​​﻿﻿‌‌‍‌​​﻿‍​​﻿​‌​﻿‍​​﻿‌‍​﻿​​‌‍​‍​﻿‌﻿​‍﻿‌​﻿‌﻿‌‍​‍​﻿‌﻿​﻿​‍​‍﻿‌​﻿‌​‌‍​‍‌‍​‌​﻿‌‌​‍﻿‌​﻿‍​‌‍​‌‌‍‌​​﻿‌‌​‍﻿‌​﻿​﻿‌‍​‍​﻿‌﻿​﻿‌﻿‌‍‌‍‌‍‌​​﻿‍‌‌‍​‌​﻿‍​‌‍‌‌​﻿‍‌‌‍​‍​﻿‍﻿‌﻿‌​‌﻿‍‌‌﻿​​‌‍‌‌​﻿﻿‌‌‍​‍‌‍﻿​‌‍﻿﻿‌‍‌﻿‌‌​​‌‍﻿﻿‌﻿​﻿‌﻿‌​​﻿‍﻿‌﻿​​‌‍​‌‌﻿‌​‌‍‍​​﻿﻿‌‌‍‌‌‌﻿‍​‌‍​﻿‌‍‌‌‌﻿​‍‌﻿​​‌﻿‌​​﻿﻿﻿‌‍​‍‌‍​‌‌﻿​﻿‌‍‌‌‌‌‌‌‌﻿​‍‌‍﻿​​﻿﻿‌‌‍‍​‌﻿‌​‌﻿‌​‌﻿​​‌﻿​﻿​‍‌‌​﻿​﻿‌​​‌​‍‌‌​﻿​‍‌​‌‍​‍‌‌​﻿​‍‌​‌‍‌‍​﻿‌‍﻿‌‌﻿​﻿​‍﻿‍‌﻿​﻿‌﻿‌​‌‍​‌‌‍​﻿‌‍‍﻿‌‍﻿﻿‌﻿‌‍‌‍‌‌‌﻿​‍‌‍‌‍‌‍﻿​‌‍﻿﻿‌﻿‌﻿​‍﻿‍‌‍​﻿‌‍﻿﻿​‍‌‍‌‍‍‌‌‍‌​​﻿﻿‌‌‍‌​​﻿‍​​﻿​‌​﻿‍​​﻿‌‍​﻿​​‌‍​‍​﻿‌﻿​‍﻿‌​﻿‌﻿‌‍​‍​﻿‌﻿​﻿​‍​‍﻿‌​﻿‌​‌‍​‍‌‍​‌​﻿‌‌​‍﻿‌​﻿‍​‌‍​‌‌‍‌​​﻿‌‌​‍﻿‌​﻿​﻿‌‍​‍​﻿‌﻿​﻿‌﻿‌‍‌‍‌‍‌​​﻿‍‌‌‍​‌​﻿‍​‌‍‌‌​﻿‍‌‌‍​‍​‍‌‍‌﻿‌​‌﻿‍‌‌﻿​​‌‍‌‌​﻿﻿‌‌‍​‍‌‍﻿​‌‍﻿﻿‌‍‌﻿‌‌​​‌‍﻿﻿‌﻿​﻿‌﻿‌​​‍‌‍‌﻿​​‌‍​‌‌﻿‌​‌‍‍​​﻿﻿‌‌‍‌‌‌﻿‍​‌‍​﻿‌‍‌‌‌﻿​‍‌﻿​​‌﻿‌​​‍‌‍‌﻿​​‌‍‌‌‌﻿​‍‌﻿​﻿‌﻿​​‌‍‌‌‌‍​﻿‌﻿‌​‌‍‍‌‌﻿‌‍‌‍‌‌​﻿﻿‌‌﻿​​‌﻿‌‌‌‍​‍‌‍﻿​‌‍‍‌‌﻿​﻿‌‍‍​‌‍‌‌‌‍‌​​‍​‍‌﻿﻿‌"}